Maruf is the best host. She is always attentive to your needs and, apart from helping you with all the necessary amenities, she has helped us plan our trip.
Maruf has become our friend. Totally recommendable.
The area also because it is close to the metro stop to go downtown and in a guarded and quiet area to rest from the madness that is Dhaka.
